- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper mentions image segmentation as one of the real-world applications of kernel spectral clustering. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the handling of large-scale data in kernel spectral clustering. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses a model-based approach to clustering and mentions the use of Error Correcting Output Codes (ECOC) encoding scheme. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper discusses the use of Incomplete Cholesky Decomposition (ICD) and regularization techniques in kernel spectral clustering.
